title: Upgrade v11.9.0-rc0 PersistenceCore
summary:
This is a proposal to do a software upgrade to [v11.9.0-rc0](https://github.com/persistenceOne/persistenceCore/releases/tag/v11.9.0-rc0).
This upgrade bumps several core dependencies, the full list can be checked [here](https://github.com/persistenceOne/persistenceCore/pull/312).
